    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"finished\"... that's a dark way to put it. but it feels right. like there's nothing left to salvage. like trying to fix something that's already been gone for a decade. it's just exhausting, carrying around this corpse of a life every single day. why bother even trying to pretend anymore?",
